stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Preview : POST /papers/generate (unsaved, id = null, + seed)
    Preview --> Preview : regenerate (new seed)
    Preview --> Saved : POST /papers (persist, re-run from seed)
    Saved --> Exported : GET /papers/{id}/export (pdf | docx)
    Exported --> Exported : re-export (export_count++)
    Saved --> [*] : delete
    Exported --> [*] : delete
    note right of Preview
        Discarded if never saved —
        no history clutter.
    end note